334
00:17:12.833 --> 00:17:14.000
-What's going on?
-It's Mpume.

335
00:17:14.083 --> 00:17:17.041
Get out! Get out. both of you! Get out!

336
00:17:17.750 --> 00:17:21.333
-Get out. Bongs! Get out of my room!
-What's going on?

337
00:17:21.416 --> 00:17:23.166
Just leave! Leave!

338
00:17:23.250 --> 00:17:27.625
What are you still doing here?
Get out! Get out. Bongs!

339
00:17:27.708 --> 00:17:28.708
-What's going on?
-Mpume.

340
00:17:28.791 --> 00:17:30.625
Oh. my gosh. Just leave.

341
00:17:30.708 --> 00:17:33.291
-Mpume! What's happening?
-My goodness! Sarah!

342
00:17:33.375 --> 00:17:35.666
-What's going on in this house?
